data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Captivating 3-Bedroom Townhome in the Desirable GATED COMMUNITY of Towns at Legacy Park. This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom CORNER-UNIT offers a harmonious blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience, all nestled in a prime location. LOCATION PERFECTION: Situated just 9 miles from the magical world of Walt Disney and with quick and easy access to I-4, attractions, world-class golf courses, shopping, and restaurants, this property promises a lifestyle of endless fun and adventure. STYLISH INTERIOR: Step inside to discover a home boasting an open floor plan and easy-to-maintain tile flooring perfect for entertaining and daily living. COMFORTABLE LIVING SPACES: The first floor features a delightful open kitchen which is a host's delight with 42" cabinets, a STAINLESS STEEL REFRIGERATOR, and a bar that overlooks the living room, dining room, and even the lanai through the large 3-panel sliding glass doors. Retreat upstairs to indulge in the comfort and beauty of the three spacious bedrooms. The home’s upstairs design also thoughtfully includes a central laundry room alongside the contemporary charm of new wood-look flooring. Step outside onto your cozy screened-in lanai, a perfect spot to unwind after a busy day. COMMUNITY AMENITIES: As a resident of Towns at Legacy Park, you will have access to a plethora of amenities, including a beautiful community pool, spa, and sundeck. Not only are you conveniently located to all the fun of the major theme parks but many other local attractions including the nearby Promenade at Sunset Walk which offers a modern shopping complex, casual eateries, and a movie theater for endless entertainment options. MOVE-IN-READY: This home is move-in ready, waiting for you to fill it with love, laughter, and memories. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this gem in Towns at Legacy Park. Schedule your private showing today and start living your dream lifestyle!
